src:
Hasil Liga 1 Indonesia Jumat Ini
01 Nov 2019, 14:12 by Tempo.co, Aditya Budiman
TEMPO.CO, Jakarta - Liga 1 Indonesia sudah memasuki pekan ke-26. Hingga Jumat, 1 November 2019 sudah ada empat laga tersaji. Salah satunya ialah Kalteng Putra melawan Persib Bandung.
Laga tersebut berakhir dengan kemenangan Persib. Tim berjuluk Maung Bandung ini menang dua gol tanpa balas. Dua gol tim Maung Bandung datang dari Kevin va Kippersluis pada menit 45+4. Lalu gol penutup dicetak oleh Ezechiel N'Douassel pada menit ke-61.
Hasil positif tersebut jadi modal bagus bagi Persib untuk menjamu PSIS Semarang di laga selanjutnya. Kini pasukan Robert Alberts berada di peringkat 8 dengan 34 poin.

text:
Indonesian League 1 results this Friday
01 Nov 2019, 14:12 by Tempo.co, Aditya Budiman
TEMPO.CO, Jakarta - League 1 of Indonesia has entered its 26th week. Until Friday, November 1, 2019 there have been four games presented. One of them is Kalteng Putra against Persib Bandung.
The match ended with the victory of Persib. The team nicknamed Maung Bandung won two goals without reply. Two of the Maung Bandung team's goals came from Kevin va Kippersluis on 45 + 4 minutes. Then the closing goal was scored by Ezechiel N'Douassel in the 61st minute.
These positive results become a good capital for Persib to host PSIS Semarang in the next fight. Now Robert Alberts's army is ranked 8th with 34 points.

Indonesia League 1 results Week 26

Barito Putera vs Borneo FC 1-0Bali United vs Persela Lamongan 1-1Badak Lampung vs Arema FC 4-3Kalteng Putra vs Persib Bandung 0-2
